Cam::

She cuddled up in Windlord's arms and whimped as she looked up at 
Blackfang.  She sniffed closer to the new bot and tried to swat at 
Blackfangs hands playfully. She then jumped down from Windlord's arms 
and transformed into bot mode. Her vocals still weren't working. She 
walked up boldly to Blackfang and reached her small hand up to shake.
